data.description: Eloquently  renovated. This house has so much to offer. No area in this home has been left untouched. From the quartz countertops to the custom staircase. Beautiful, uniform flooring, and great appliances. The bathrooms offer taste and style with fully tiled master shower,  stone basin sink and gorgeous faucets. Almost everything in home has been replaced. Beautiful updated lighting fixtures, and faux beams give this home a cozy feeling. The porch has also weatherproof boarding. The spacious backyard gives you some space to relax. Hot tub conveys. So close to schools, shopping and downtown Winchester. Call today for your personal tour.
